    "body": "It seems it depends on the content of the prompt.\n\nIn my case (`Powershell 7.5.1`), when the prompt contains git info, after two fast `Ctrl+C`, the prompt is broken.\nIf I change the directory to a folder without a git project, the prompt works fine.\n\n![Image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/291f12ea-9038-4659-8f74-449f73e755a6)",
